{"tid":2382362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁子超：果欄一帶難圍封應強制檢測","createTime":"2021-01-27T08:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T09:33:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"38570aa07a2d778f2b155f0fa4936ef01f7776a5","tid":2382362,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q.btxXvZT5ifAvEeLJC1Cw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/T6FRR8isJPDuf3RhVW7QOA--~B/aD0xMDgwO3c9MTkyMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/RTHK-LEUNG-210125-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq.btxXvZT5ifAvEeLJC1Cw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FT6FRR8isJPDuf3RhVW7QOA--~B%2FaD0xMDgwO3c9MTkyMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FRTHK-LEUNG-210125-10.jpg&h=d3141c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】油麻地果欄一帶確診個案增加，呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超稱，圍封果欄較為困難，建議當局應該安排該區工作人員及居民強制檢測，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良也認為，不需要圍封果欄。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超：「如果做突撃圍封，商戶的損失可能相當大，如果不突撃圍封果欄，不合作的人又如何確保。圍封到底可做些甚麼，我想比較簡單是覺得有問題，就將該區域就派車去做強制檢測，若是邊緣地方也提供願檢盡檢，發現有大廈影響則再做強檢。」<br />\n<br />\n何栢良：「重點不是圍封，重點是需要檢測的人盡快完成，及需要檢疫的人盡快找出送去檢疫，如果在那地方短時間內應檢測的檢測，應檢疫的檢疫，是不需要圍封。」"},{"pid":"3e4b8d4049ac5dbf222e6b678c5b8907d19542dc","tid":2382362,"uid":973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"果欄就唔圍封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他商戶就可以損失<br />\n果欄就唔可以<br />\n笑死"},{"pid":"33ce4c8e0d2219deac0de201425b5db842037396","tid":2382362,"uid":25673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e4b8d4049ac5dbf222e6b678c5b8907d19542dc","tid":2382362,"uid":973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"果欄就唔圍封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他商戶就可以損失<br />\n果欄就唔可以<br />\n笑死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"可能又係同病毒傾好唔搞果欄呢"},{"pid":"bcb7fc8d6816cc8718e268b10516b47074e9a384","tid":2382362,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"果欄都係黑底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da884160071c33512a8adba9c8ff3c8a9d698de9","tid":2382362,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"正潔鳩專家, 唔圍封你點知係咪個個都有測呀, 又等佢自願獻身呀?"},{"pid":"bca9624eae1132d5058207619bde05ec2d1930ba","tid":2382362,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"怕俾班黑社會斬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd90536a86c3d19bbe131bd685531b5a03548799","tid":2382362,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"唔係好打得㗎咩喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迎難而上至係㗎嘛"},{"pid":"8e5a931aca7124ed2c71691f828926b0c8a0ecbc","tid":2382362,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb7fc8d6816cc8718e268b10516b47074e9a384","tid":2382362,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"果欄都係黑底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"五百蚊 一盒車厘子<br />\n唔賠一定斬人"},{"pid":"71d9134143e81cac3a91ae3de9b7c09f47373eb0","tid":2382362,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e5a931